name: Advanced Seminar in Gender and Family
description: This course offers an in-depth examination of selected topics in Gender and Family. Check the department website for details at: www.utsc.utoronto.ca/sociology/programs.
prerequisites: [[10.0 credits and SOCB05H3 and [1.0 credit from the following: SOCB30H3, SOCB42H3, SOCB43H3, SOCB47H3, (SOCC39H3)]] or [8.0 credits, including WSTB05H3 and enrolment in the Major in Women's and Gender Studies]
